Get Inspired: Jade Jones on why she got into and loves taekwondo

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
"I love the fact that if you switch off for a second you can get knocked out," says Olympic taekwondo gold medallist Jade Jones.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
